{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012cMEfYDsoNgp8xXRAZZxp4","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Project Settings File: config.toml\n     2→\n     3→**Date:** 2026-03-06\n     4→**Status:** Design\n     5→\n     6→## Problem\n     7→\n     8→The per-project settings file is `.cloche/config` with no extension, making it\n     9→ambiguous and inconsistent with the TOML library in use.\n    10→\n    11→## Change\n    12→\n    13→Rename to `.cloche/config.toml`. No backwards compatibility with the old filename.\n    14→\n    15→## Default file (created by `cloche init`)\n    16→\n    17→```toml\n    18→# Cloche project configuration\n    19→\n    20→[orchestration]\n    21→concurrency        = 1\n    22→stagger_seconds    = 1.0\n    23→# list_tasks_command = \"bash .cloche/scripts/ready-tasks.sh\"\n    24→# dedup_seconds    = 300\n    25→\n    26→[evolution]\n    27→enabled           = true\n    28→debounce_seconds  = 30\n    29→min_confidence    = \"medium\"\n    30→max_prompt_bullets = 50\n    31→```\n    32→\n    33→Notes:\n    34→- `orchestration.concurrency` defaults to `1` (single run at a time).\n    35→- `orchestration.stagger_seconds` adds delay between consecutive launches (default `1.0`).\n    36→- `orchestration.list_tasks_command` (optional) is a shell command that outputs a JSON array of\n    37→  task objects (`[{\"id\":\"...\",\"title\":\"...\",\"description\":\"...\"}]`). When set, the daemon\n    38→  picks tasks and passes the ID via `CLOCHE_TASK_ID` env var.\n    39→- `orchestration.dedup_seconds` (default `300`) prevents reassignment of the same task ID\n    40→  within the timeout window.\n    41→- Commented-out keys show optional overrides that rarely need changing.\n    42→\n    43→## Code changes\n    44→\n    45→| File | Change |\n    46→|------|--------|\n    47→| `internal/config/config.go` | `Load()`: change path from `\"config\"` to `\"config.toml\"` |\n    48→| `cmd/cloche/init.go` | Add `config.toml` to the files created by init |\n    49→| `.cloche/config` (existing file in this repo) | Rename to `.cloche/config.toml` |\n    50→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01JUnpJzSHuhmadkgcFGRrK6","session_id":"a1496100-58bb-4933-86a8-269a722f19f5","uuid":"ac4ee030-64c5-4222-be35-06f6f7b2b24e"}
